      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.203-17</ph> Contractor Employee
Whistleblower Rights and Requirement To Inform Employees of Whistleblower
Rights.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3065e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed
in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1123984.dita#i1123984"
                     base="i1123984"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">3.908-9</xref>
            </ph>, insert the
following clause:</p>
         <p rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020"
            outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps"
            class="- topic/p "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>Contractor
Employee Whistleblower Rights and Requirement to Inform Employees
of Whistleblower Rights (Jun 2020)<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 52.203-17 by—
a. Revising the date of the clause;?></p>
         <ol id="d3042e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3065e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  This
contract and employees working on this contract will be subject
to the whistleblower rights and remedies in the pilot program on
Contractor employee whistleblower protections established at <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C. 4712</xref> by
section 828 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal
Year 2013 (Pub. L. 112-239) and <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>Federal
Acquisition Regulation (FAR) <xref href="FAR-i1123923.dita#i1123923"
                           base="i1123923"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">3.908</xref>.<?FM MARKER [Why] b. Removing from paragraph (a) “FAR 3.908” and adding “Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) 3.908” in its place;?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3065e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  The Contractor
shall inform its employees in writing, in the predominant language
of the workforce, of employee whistleblower rights and protections
under <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C. 4712</xref>, as
described in section <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>FAR <xref href="FAR-i1123923.dita#i1123923"
                           base="i1123923"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">3.908</xref>.<?FM MARKER [Why] c.Removing from paragraph (b) “section 3.908 of the Federal Acquisition Regulation” and adding “FAR 3.908” in its place; and?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3065e50" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  The Contractor
shall insert the substance of this clause, including this paragraph
(c), in all subcontracts over the simplified acquisition <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>threshold, as defined in FAR <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                           base="i1125359"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref> on the date of subcontract
award.<?FM MARKER [Why] d.Removing from paragraph (c) “threshold.” and adding “threshold, as defined in FAR 2.101 on the date of subcontract award.” in its place.?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
